Priority: extra
Maintainer: Daniel Stonier <d.stonier@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9.0.0), ros-kinetic-catkin, ros-kinetic-ecl-config, ros-kinetic-ecl-license, ros-kinetic-ecl-threads
Homepage: http://ros.org/wiki/ecl_sigslots
Standards-Version: 3.9.2

Package: ros-kinetic-ecl-sigslots
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ros-kinetic-ecl-config, ros-kinetic-ecl-license, ros-kinetic-ecl-threads
Description: Provides a signal/slot mechanism (in the same vein as qt sigslots, boost::signals etc for intra-process communication.
 These include some improvements - they do not need a preprocessor, are fully type safe, allow for simple connections via a posix style string identifier and are multithread-safe.
